{"tid":1491573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登竟然冇人講 maglite？！！","createTime":"2019-08-20T13:06:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T16:48:24.000Z","uid":123991,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"af60baa1148a28d7f04fc9505da8d2ef2e3f8cd6","tid":1491573,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:06:44.000Z","msg":"香港人熱愛運動<br />\n行山又游水<br />\n竟然冇人傾行得山又防水嘅 mgalite 電筒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每一個 D 代表入幾多粒 D-cell battery, 即係香港人口中嘅&quot;中size電&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eyeu7Vg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Feyeu7Vg.jpg&h=0e6cce46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為行山愛好者緊係要買 6D, 唔記得換電點算 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nmgalite 6D 官網:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.maglite.com/shop/flashlights/full-size-flashlights/maglite-6-cell-d-flashlight.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.maglite.com%2Fshop%2Fflashlights%2Ffull-size-flashlights%2Fmaglite-6-cell-d-flashlight.html&d=TRt9Hu9y5T%2Bqj71zgJeH9jk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=b7fedc43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.maglite.com/shop/flashlights/full-size-flashlights/maglite-6-cell-d-flashlight.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成支 aluminum 做, 趺得多都唔會爛 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ykF6qH6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FykF6qH6.jpg&h=d85f1b2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無奈有d 長咗小小咁架, 不過最緊要行山安全  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yhtcmgF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyhtcmgF.jpg&h=58e4139b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nmaglite 品質有保證, 一齊黎睇下佢嘅製造過程幾咁嚴謹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wXWxzUkC_c8?t=53\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be